item.value: Ken and Sunny, as we discussed previously, we have large of number of customers who is margin account and they donot have the funds of 100 shares ,we discussed that they would be able to subscription under 10 time leverage. we found that more than 800 customer's order of 09988.HK was rejected, we need to resubmit the files and we need their subscriptions are effected. Could you please help us to handle the problem?
Are you ready to send us multiple files a day including 9988.HK? This ensure we have sufficient funding prepared and allocated on our end.

Thanks for your confirmation，we’ll double check with our related colleague. But may I know 5:00 BJT is the final ending time in the following HK IPOs? Or just because it’s during the system test period which you referred to yesterday?

At this stage we are closing specific HK IPOs at 05:00 BJT to facilitate our testing. Once we have reviewed the impact on all the related processes/operations we will communicate what you can expect going forward. Hopefully we will be in a position to confirm later next week.
Your team monitoring the API files may have noticed that in our latest OpenIPOs file
After the test is completed will send additional correspondence to further outline the changes we are making and confirm any revised operational timelines going forward.

You are welcome to make the files you submitted this am your final ones as planned but if you would like make further submissions throughout the day for this IPO, please do so. Just make sure you let us know if you decide to make additional submissions otherwise we will consider the files you submitted this am as your final confirmed numbers
